{% set notes %}
{% spaceless %}
  <bolt-ol>
    <bolt-li>The Table Element is designed to work with both Twig and vanilla HTML (Twig is the recommended method).</bolt-li>
    <bolt-li>Refer to the <a href="{{ link['elements-table-top-side-headers'] }}" class="e-bolt-text-link">Table Element with Top and Side Headers</a> page for information on adding the headers.</bolt-li>
    <bolt-li><strong>Twig:</strong> Use the <code>footer</code> prop to render a footer row.</bolt-li>
    <bolt-li><strong>HTML:</strong> Add a <code>&lt;tfoot&gt;</code> to the <code>&lt;table&gt;</code> to render a footer row.</bolt-li>
  </bolt-ol>
{% endspaceless %}
{% endset %}

